p><p>Fully installed projects starting around $4,800.<\/p>","button_label":"EXPLORE","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/convert-my-fireplace"}},"0ddb2b9e-75ac-4f9a-84f2-9151b7d9497c":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/fireside_add_fireplace.jpg","title":"ADD A NEW FIREPLACE","text":"<p>Install a new fireplace in nearly any area of the home. Fireplaces can be added to indoor or outdoor spaces and come in a variety of designs to complement every style. <\/p><p>Fully installed projects starting around $6,700. <\/p>","button_label":"EXPLORE","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/add-new-fireplace"}},"034a8b1e-6c40-45cb-8e9c-f616000760d3":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/fireside-family-brunch-fit-lg.png","title":"REPLACE YOUR FIREPLACE","text":"<p>Transform your existing fireplace into a fresh design with the added convenience of smart technology. Update just your fireplace or the entire wall - including mantel and stone - for a stunning remodel. <\/p><p>Fully installed projects starting around $6,900.<\/p>","button_label":"EXPLORE","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/replace-my-fireplace"}}},"block_order":["fe96a1f4-43b6-4294-9137-7135c56f25e5","0ddb2b9e-75ac-4f9a-84f2-9151b7d9497c","034a8b1e-6c40-45cb-8e9c-f616000760d3"],"settings":{"reveal-on":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"vertical_text":"G<br>A<br>T<br>H<br>E<br>R"}},"16528108123d0a1179":{"type":"featured-text","settings":{"reveal-on":true,"padding_top":80,"padding_bottom":80,"mobile-padding-top":80,"mobile-padding-bottom":80,"bg_color":"#3d484e","heading_text_alignment":"center","title":"Fireplace Repair & Preventative Maintenance","paragraph_text_alignment":"center","content":"<p>Our team has over 100 years of combined technical experience to help keep your fireplace looking and working like new with repair services or preventative maintenance.  <\/p>","button_text_alignment":"center","button_label":"Request Service","open-new-window":false,"but